# Keep large runtime data and local cruft OUT of the Docker build context and
# images. Without this, `COPY . .` bakes data/ (GBs of OSM/GTFS) and pelias/data
# (tens of GB of Elasticsearch index + downloads) into every image — producing
# 20GB+ images. The image only needs source, scripts, import assets, and config.
node_modules
.git
.gitignore

# Runtime data — never belongs in an image
data/
pelias/

# Local env / logs / editor cruft
.env
*.log
.DS_Store
